Fix slow motion lagging bug
issue.body:
Pretty sure it has to do with when the two particle systems get close and interact with each other.  This may be due to collisions or just rendering.

Fixable by: 

Messing with values and lowering numParticles and speed.  Should be able to achieve about the same effect with many less particles.

Look at the collision settings

Worst case scenario, disable them when too close to each other and re-enable them when far enough apart.  This should be done in a way that the player shouldn't notice
